name: White Teeth Filling
description: White fillings can also be called dental composite and they are the tooth-coloured resins used to fill cavities.

name: Wisdom Teeth Removal
description: The pain and swelling should subside more each day surgery. The second day surgery is the worst day for swelling.

name: Teeth Replacement
description: Dental implants are surgically placed in your jawbone, where they serve as the roots of missing teeth.

name: Crown Dental
description: Dental crowns are tooth-shaped caps that can be placed over your tooth. Think of it like a snug hat for your tooth.

name: Bridge Dental
description: A dental bridge is a commonly used dental device that consists of one or more artificial teeth made from resin.

name: Root Canal
description: Root canal is a treatment to repair and save a badly damaged or infected tooth instead of removing it.
